- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new method for generating mel-spectrograms in parallel, which can be seen as a control problem.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses neural networks for speech synthesis.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new method for text-to-speech synthesis using deep learning.
